  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      There is a decrease in the amount of blood components used during cardiac surgery in the
      last four years. As the hemovigilance team of the investigators' Hospital the investigators
      want to find out the causes and effects of this decrease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
